<body>
    <h1>Task 12 -RAD</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <hr local-id=3D"82312a216c8f">
<h1 local-id=3D"28d3a37ad96b" id=3D"Task12-RAD-1.Introduction">1. Introduct=
ion</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"43064e2efdf4" id=3D"Task12-RAD-1.1Purpose">1.1 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"795d987b0a0c">The purpose of this document is to define the =
requirements for implementing a monitoring and alerting system for the Book=
store API.</p>
<p local-id=3D"156afc135142">The monitoring system will provide visibility =
into API performance, error rates, and HTTP response patterns. This will he=
lp the operations team quickly detect issues, analyze API behavior, and res=
pond to failures effectively.</p>
<p local-id=3D"bbf3f15d4283">The document is intended for DevOps engineers,=
 developers, and operations teams responsible for maintaining and monitorin=
g the API infrastructure.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"db88eb917b5c">
<h2 local-id=3D"84df0f791a4a" id=3D"Task12-RAD-1.2Scope">1.2 Scope</h2>
<p local-id=3D"75bdb29f4b46">The scope of this project includes designing a=
nd implementing a monitoring solution that tracks the health and performanc=
e of the Bookstore API.</p>
<p local-id=3D"dda0c332bc09">The monitoring setup will include:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"da7b14370ba8">
<li local-id=3D"8d814a48c065">
<p local-id=3D"ff1e1b1f2a12">Creating a monitoring dashboard for API metric=
s</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3482e8142b8d">
<p local-id=3D"5bfdc14c7dcc">Tracking HTTP response status codes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b9636211cd10">
<p local-id=3D"2d1653a4eb57">Monitoring API error rates</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"89da31b12bfd">
<p local-id=3D"6ba9aa94eadd">Visualizing request patterns over time</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"af646990acf2">
<p local-id=3D"602095b5decd">Configuring alerts for abnormal API behavior</=
p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"81a379187ca7">The monitoring system will help the team quick=
ly detect problems such as increasing error rates, abnormal traffic pattern=
s, or API unavailability.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ef650838cb26">The project does <strong>not include full prod=
uction monitoring systems such as distributed tracing or advanced APM tools=
</strong>, as the focus is basic operational observability.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"b6852b614feb">
<h2 local-id=3D"790fd4945859" id=3D"Task12-RAD-1.3Definitions,Acronyms,andA=
bbreviations">1.3 Definitions, Acronyms, and Abbreviations</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"2=
