</div>
<hr local-id=3D"dbae1fcc6c93">
<h2 local-id=3D"376708c2481f" id=3D"Task12-RAD-1.4References">1.4 Reference=
s</h2>
<p local-id=3D"c3c8c655800a">Bookstore API Repository<br><a href=3D"https:/=
/github.com/pushkar-iamops/bookstore-api" local-id=3D"77d65f679f54" data-ca=
rd-appearance=3D"inline" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://g=
ithub.com/pushkar-iamops/bookstore-api</a></p>
<p local-id=3D"3622d1ddc18d">AWS Documentation<br><a href=3D"https://docs.a=
ws.amazon.com" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://docs.aws.am=
azon.com</a></p>
<p local-id=3D"b79e1086a74b">HTTP Status Codes<br><a href=3D"https://develo=
per.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Status" local-id=3D"9dec8cf37e1b" data-=
card-appearance=3D"inline" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https:/=
/developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Status</a></p>
<hr local-id=3D"201e7deda025">
<h2 local-id=3D"766497de5e99" id=3D"Task12-RAD-1.5Overview">1.5 Overview</h=
2>
<p local-id=3D"f2cf8efb41f5">This document is organized into the following =
sections:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"822397f8e8a4">
<li local-id=3D"bc2d043edad4">
<p local-id=3D"ab38618590ad">Section 1 introduces the purpose and scope of =
the document.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"daf57a97aa09">
<p local-id=3D"d91007c5da9c">Section 2 provides the project overview and ob=
jectives.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e0274b060341">
<p local-id=3D"56ccf3fe3534">Section 3 defines functional requirements incl=
uding monitoring use cases.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e4211db2d40f">
<p local-id=3D"3494eb4ab446">Section 4 describes non-functional requirement=
s such as reliability and usability.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6e719f7f99be">
<p local-id=3D"35764f3c4d5c">Section 5 lists assumptions and dependencies.<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"48c3c63d4bd5">
<p local-id=3D"50a4d74225a7">Section 6 discusses potential risks and mitiga=
tion strategies.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"2670a39650b2">
<h1 local-id=3D"85bd24519a94" id=3D"Task12-RAD-2.ProjectOverview">2. Projec=
t Overview</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"f818b2caf556" id=3D"Task12-RAD-2.1ProjectObjectives">2.1 Pr=
oject Objectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"c0abe953abe4">The main objectives of this project are:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"2e703002bf41">
<li local-id=3D"715193171b95">
<p local-id=3D"c1b938cfb3be">Provide visibility into API health and perform=
ance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a0316372c405">
<p local-id=3D"d196124ddd01">Monitor HTTP response status codes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8d3dad3d082d">
<p local-id=3D"cfa042199e95">Track API error rates and response patterns</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"715542aaee4a">
<p local-id=3D"b9920947e947">Detect abnormal API behavior through alerts</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"0f6ae490b22b">
<p local-id=3D"58fb9f6fe40e">Enable faster troubleshooting for operational =
teams</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"6de8a5cab275">
<h2 local-id=3D"9e925b68e2f7" id=3D"Task12-RAD-2.2BusinessGoals">2.2 Busine=
ss Goals</h2>
<p local-id=3D"2675d9d5874d">The business goals of the monitoring system in=
clude:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"65527aabf44e">
<li local-id=3D"65a34343c575">
<p local-id=3D"50b47633cc65">Improving observability of the API</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9762f42337d5">
<p local-id=3D"719829a77cd9">Detecting API failures quickly</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bff48f4f23e7">
<p local-id=3D"6da3bad2ad59">Supporting operational decision making</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"62edff6a6ab5">
<p local-id=3D"e8b3478d49c1">Reducing downtime caused by undetected issues<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"41d62849ec3e">
<p local-id=3D"6b2893e22ae8">Providing clear monitoring dashboards for revi=
ew meetings</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"213aa7a333d7">
<h2 local-id=3D"300e8f7e054f" id=3D"Task12-RAD-2.3Background">2.3 Backgroun=
d</h2>
<p local-id=3D"6033c22a9e09">ABC Technologies has successfully deployed the=
 Bookstore API. However, the operations team currently lacks visibility int=
o how the API behaves in real time.</p>
<p local-id=3D"48f93fe0a76a">Without proper monitoring, it is difficult to =
identify problems such as rising error rates, API failures, or unusual traf=
fic patterns.</p>
<p local-id=3D"feb694e412d3">To improve operational awareness, the team req=
uires a monitoring solution that tracks API metrics such as request count, =
HTTP status codes, and error rates.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8e910e12f603">By implementing monitoring dashboards and aler=
ts, the team can quickly detect abnormal API behavior and respond to incide=
nts more effectively.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"b21355f22b1a">
<h2 local-id=3D"91d218cc7259" id=3D"Task12-RAD-2.4Constraints">2.4 Constrai=
nts</h2>
<p local-id=3D"eb5f353df0d1">The following constraints apply to this projec=
t:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"eba2983163c1">
<li local-id=3D"2a92eae1c27f">
<p local-id=3D"aa88190ff1e3">The monitoring solution must be implemented wi=
thin <strong>3 hours</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"67d4a3286aeb">
<p local-id=3D"acb246ce544f">The dashboard must be simple and easy to under=
stand</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b057defd729e">
<p local-id=3D"dc9f9ad8454e">Alerts must be configured for critical API fai=
lure conditions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d9fce08080c8">
<p local-id=3D"e92caae084a8">The system should rely on existing API logs or=
 metrics</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"0d281a9b7170">
<h1 local-id=3D"5cc696bc0c62" id=3D"Task12-RAD-3.FunctionalRequirements">3.=
 Functional Requirements</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"59a068200d55" id=3D"Task12-RAD-3.1UseCaseDiagram">3.1 Use C=
ase Diagram</h2>
<p local-id=3D"67a4eaa84384">The use case diagram illustrates how the DevOp=
s engineer interacts with the monitoring system to track API behavior and c=
onfigure alerts.</p>
<p local-id=3D"e76692ae2169">The system enables monitoring of API metrics, =
visualization of response patterns, and alerting for abnormal conditions.</=
p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper conf=
luence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-=
center" alt=3D"Untitled Diagram.drawio (11)-20260311-092110.png" width=3D"4=
68" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"3f185d387179098fc2b81f35b1736421313b6b2b0738384=
c0c49579a893dd467" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/down=
