<hr local-id=3D"357cbc9e898c">
<h1 local-id=3D"3dbfc2596d7e" id=3D"Task12-RAD-3.2UseCases">3.2 Use Cases</=
h1>
<hr local-id=3D"612d438f1c4b">
<h1 local-id=3D"68bc257796a4" id=3D"Task12-RAD-3.2.1UseCase1:CreateAPIMonit=
oringDashboard">3.2.1 Use Case 1: Create API Monitoring Dashboard</h1>
<p local-id=3D"e9099487ed1e"><strong>Description</strong><br>
Create a monitoring dashboard that displays API metrics and response patter=
ns.</p>
<p local-id=3D"fefb9d5ca57a"><strong>Actors</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"411f254038c6"><strong>Preconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"b50d8db3511d">
<li local-id=3D"2a9ac260a40f">
<p local-id=3D"f0e787b83dd5">API logs or metrics are available</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4d21fd7e526f">
<p local-id=3D"674d7350f616">Monitoring platform is accessible</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4d784e51be55"><strong>Postconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3d8914b477aa">
<li local-id=3D"711c33547795">
<p local-id=3D"4bf157a8150c">Dashboard displays API metrics and response st=
atistics</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"15f0ff1cd852"><strong>Flow of Events</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"2751a211e031">
<li local-id=3D"df65d8641af7">
<p local-id=3D"50ddd682b282">Access the monitoring platform.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"328bc779e11f">
<p local-id=3D"9adf0828648b">Create a new dashboard.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f9de3933d870">
<p local-id=3D"47020642462a">Add widgets for request count, response status=
 codes, and error rates.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"27f40861c400">
<p local-id=3D"d43996eedbd9">Configure visualizations such as line charts a=
nd bar charts.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"67691c2f15d4">
<p local-id=3D"3a95bcf24153">Save and verify dashboard functionality.</p></=
li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"01ef18626573"><strong>Alternative Flows</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"a7f175e515b4">
<li local-id=3D"c62cb4a9d631">
<p local-id=3D"d79f87f9b057">Metrics unavailable =E2=86=92 verify log colle=
ction configuration.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a5b2abcea1ea">
<h1 local-id=3D"93fb3564330a" id=3D"Task12-RAD-3.2.2UseCase2:MonitorHTTPSta=
tusCodeDistribution">3.2.2 Use Case 2: Monitor HTTP Status Code Distributio=
n</h1>
<p local-id=3D"c675df2ef6c8"><strong>Description</strong><br>
Track and visualize API responses based on HTTP status codes.</p>
<p local-id=3D"0487df8cfe8a"><strong>Actors</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"aebb2573761a"><strong>Preconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"4de2c301bbe5">
<li local-id=3D"dccccac2654b">
<p local-id=3D"ce7b5ffbc7ca">API request logs are available</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"998ed5ff6533"><strong>Postconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"eb7adb6430cf">
<li local-id=3D"d36838fd3ef5">
<p local-id=3D"735df4d3a366">Dashboard displays distribution of 2xx, 4xx, a=
nd 5xx responses</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f6a5a7d79991"><strong>Flow of Events</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"6329ea93ec92">
<li local-id=3D"a2dae771126c">
<p local-id=3D"2402c9a56aaf">Collect API response metrics.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c3a404e89164">
<p local-id=3D"fc3566a9ba60">Categorize responses by HTTP status code group=
s.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f086e8208b09">
<p local-id=3D"933b05ccf114">Display response counts using visualizations.<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e2d22c67a53d">
<p local-id=3D"075132435e95">Track trends over time.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"5246bca099d6"><strong>Alternative Flows</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"656556c8d748">
<li local-id=3D"3d6a057485f3">
<p local-id=3D"776c0d86dd85">Incorrect metrics =E2=86=92 verify log parsing=
 configuration.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"ff4befdc637d">
<h1 local-id=3D"e57634deed30" id=3D"Task12-RAD-3.2.3UseCase3:MonitorAPIErro=
rRate">3.2.3 Use Case 3: Monitor API Error Rate</h1>
<p local-id=3D"65c061d757ea"><strong>Description</strong><br>
Track and analyze the percentage of failed API requests.</p>
<p local-id=3D"3f62a4ddd1c2"><strong>Actors</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"887b249a34b8"><strong>Preconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"626ab549d1ad">
<li local-id=3D"2428ae955f8e">
<p local-id=3D"90df35c4c9e7">API request metrics are available</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"aa6fe369e715"><strong>Postconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"7c7f7ba77913">
<li local-id=3D"a86812537e25">
<p local-id=3D"f2d492ecb7ff">Dashboard displays error rate trends</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"744015d61d9f"><strong>Flow of Events</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"32fd46fddab0">
<li local-id=3D"68eaf81496ef">
<p local-id=3D"0230c8580b02">Calculate error rate based on total requests a=
nd failed responses.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"24bf0766711c">
<p local-id=3D"26cb9456bf1d">Display error rate using graphs.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0eed25f08baa">
<p local-id=3D"cf2fd534e2df">Track changes in error rate over time.</p></li=
>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"344c2751623d"><strong>Alternative Flows</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"693406b86c3e">
<li local-id=3D"deba8cc1d29e">
<p local-id=3D"c456be4f7295">Missing error metrics =E2=86=92 verify monitor=
ing configuration.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"3fb4f74a9461">
<h1 local-id=3D"335283c91be9" id=3D"Task12-RAD-3.2.4UseCase4:ConfigureAlert=
sforAPIFailures">3.2.4 Use Case 4: Configure Alerts for API Failures</h1>
<p local-id=3D"0dfcd7ae6635"><strong>Description</strong><br>
Configure automated alerts to detect abnormal API behavior.</p>
<p local-id=3D"e7446d1629f2"><strong>Actors</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"8c5786a46f84"><strong>Preconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"292557508574">
<li local-id=3D"38c12d76f905">
<p local-id=3D"30dbd28593a9">Monitoring metrics are available</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c67580f7370b"><strong>Postconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"6e6a1ea263c7">
<li local-id=3D"671d92882adc">
<p local-id=3D"924223f4a736">Alerts are triggered when thresholds are excee=
ded</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"844062d920a8"><strong>Flow of Events</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"f9e7afd7756f">
<li local-id=3D"f1e6a5e31f98">
<p local-id=3D"9f14248d175d">Define alert thresholds.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b393f07c01fc">
<p local-id=3D"16c8ebffec84">Configure alerts for high 5xx error rates.</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"5a5106074adc">
<p local-id=3D"1abab54d845e">Configure alerts for excessive 4xx responses.<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bf0551502e14">
<p local-id=3D"a4b28a23d157">Configure alerts for API unavailability.</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"dc2e578708d5">
<p local-id=3D"674d4f9194bc">Save alert rules.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"3db744f658e5"><strong>Alternative Flows</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"fb2d1976c343">
<li local-id=3D"d279792c69db">
<p local-id=3D"1f43330852be">Incorrect thresholds =E2=86=92 adjust alert co=
nfiguration.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e49ac8594313">
<h1 local-id=3D"cb930f88caf6" id=3D"Task12-RAD-4.Non-FunctionalRequirements=
">4. Non-Functional Requirements</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"9bb7cd3dd2f6" id=3D"Task12-RAD-4.1PerformanceRequirements">=
4.1 Performance Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"1bc883e5520b">
<li local-id=3D"ee62824e56a8">
<p local-id=3D"4b948689be69">Monitoring dashboards should update metrics re=
gularly.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c8fc612612b7">
<p local-id=3D"7aefbe1e1b43">Alerts should trigger quickly when thresholds =
are exceeded.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"45388a3cab89">
<h2 local-id=3D"caa047754fd8" id=3D"Task12-RAD-4.2SecurityRequirements">4.2=
 Security Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"5985577afa4b">
<li local-id=3D"c2cb05fba69f">
<p local-id=3D"f8a66db36234">Monitoring dashboards should only be accessibl=
e to authorized users.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8c7fa056cb4a">
<p local-id=3D"bbcdf5d4a53d">Sensitive API data should not be exposed in da=
shboards.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"4d53fa43632c">
<h2 local-id=3D"3e68a36afa51" id=3D"Task12-RAD-4.3UsabilityRequirements">4.=
3 Usability Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"911c62d6c7d2">
<li local-id=3D"3e99c7598bd5">
<p local-id=3D"441b5e221e78">The dashboard must be simple and easy to under=
stand.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f17762ba9c87">
<p local-id=3D"667d65479956">Visualizations must clearly represent API heal=
th.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"89fdb9cfaaff">
<p local-id=3D"b79f8612eca8">Metrics should be organized logically.</p></li=
>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"72b2482e8cd1">
<h2 local-id=3D"8d23bc5c0b4b" id=3D"Task12-RAD-4.4ReliabilityRequirements">=
4.4 Reliability Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"6d5a79ea8504">
<li local-id=3D"5a5eafd94c8b">
<p local-id=3D"0f3a70a29e37">Monitoring metrics should be continuously avai=
lable.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8b592eb2a07d">
<p local-id=3D"e5f5c6608f92">Alerts must trigger reliably when abnormal beh=
avior occurs.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e2d2e7a18e33">
<h2 local-id=3D"b873aa2ba94c" id=3D"Task12-RAD-4.5ComplianceRequirements">4=
.5 Compliance Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"88a9e8985342">
<li local-id=3D"82f2097283d5">
<p local-id=3D"73d1f1358fda">Monitoring configuration should follow cloud s=
ecurity best practices.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5fef8fe4c78d">
<p local-id=3D"b8f7cac7ef7d">Logs must be stored securely.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"8539b82fe156">
<h1 local-id=3D"f38a6df9c138" id=3D"Task12-RAD-5.AssumptionsandDependencies=
">5. Assumptions and Dependencies</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"d4cb70b509e8" id=3D"Task12-RAD-5.1Assumptions">5.1 Assumpti=
ons</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"6c38c5b5677c">
<li local-id=3D"5be91bc65e05">
<p local-id=3D"a75d7a021db8">API logs and metrics are available.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f4cabd0bf180">
<p local-id=3D"bca98bbb0099">Monitoring tools can access API data.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"108b90c2542c">
<p local-id=3D"2bfdaecfd997">The operations team will regularly review the =
dashboard.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e3bb4be66d62">
<h2 local-id=3D"35f64404e37a" id=3D"Task12-RAD-5.2Dependencies">5.2 Depende=
ncies</h2>
<p local-id=3D"36d3bed9e52a">The monitoring system depends on:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b21e4b7a160b">
<li local-id=3D"c14045d59f5d">
<p local-id=3D"44ba35fa6234">API log availability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0f1f2599b9de">
<p local-id=3D"b2e6806d015a">Monitoring platform availability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cb7c8f37965e">
<p local-id=3D"2f9424b78c12">Network connectivity between monitoring tools =
and API services</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"57519eb6d43a">
<h1 local-id=3D"a1c216f84c52" id=3D"Task12-RAD-6.RiskAnalysis">6. Risk Anal=
ysis</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"63eeb4090391" id=3D"Task12-RAD-6.1RiskIdentification">6.1 R=
isk Identification</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"8=
d1046c1-0b5a-41ec-b8ad-5032d9a91f05" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"708b3c21e1bf">
